        "experience.title" : "Professional Experience",
        "experience.description": "This section provides an overview of my professional experience.",

        "experience.job0.place": "ACTEAM-IT / Mondial Relay",
        "experience.job0.date": "<strong>2 months</strong> - June 2023 to July 2023",
        "experience.job0.title": "Data-oriented Full-stack Developer",
        "experience.job0.desc.p1": "During my internship at ACTEAM-IT in Roubaix, I had the opportunity to work on three major projects that allowed me to develop a wide range of full-stack development skills. The first project involved the development of a web application for Mondial Relay to generate delivery driver compensation scenarios, the second was the creation of a random data generator for ACTEAM-IT's MECA application, and the third was the development of an internal financial performance indicator application leveraging Dolibarr data. My main missions included:",
        "experience.job0.desc.p2": "<li>Design and full-stack development of a web application for Mondial Relay, including a Python/FastAPI backend and a React frontend.</li><li>Creation of an innovative data generator using the OpenAI API to generate realistic test data.</li><li>Development of a financial analysis application with data visualization for management.</li><li>Collaboration with international teams and project management in complete autonomy.</li>",
        "experience.job0.desc.p3": "This experience allowed me to significantly strengthen my full-stack development, project management, and data analysis skills while working in a stimulating and innovative professional environment. I notably acquired expertise in using modern technologies and managing complex projects autonomously.",

        "experience.job1.place": "ACTEAM-IT",
        "experience.job1.date": "<strong>3 months</strong> - June 2023 to August 2023",
        "experience.job1.title": "Full-stack web developer",
        "experience.job1.desc.p1": "During my internship at ACTEAM-IT, a renowned IT expertise company located in Roubaix, I had the opportunity to actively participate in the design and development of an internal application dedicated to contract budget management. My main role as a React web developer was to:",
        "experience.job1.desc.p2": "<li>Analyze business needs and translate functional requirements into technical specifications.</li><li>Design and implement innovative front-end solutions using React.</li><li>Collaborate closely with the project team to ensure alignment between design, user experience, and business logic.</li><li>Ensure application maintenance and optimization to meet evolving business needs.</li>",
        "experience.job1.desc.p3": "This experience not only allowed me to refine my technical skills, but also to develop a methodical and professional approach to tackle complex IT challenges in a constantly evolving business context.",

        "experience.job2.place": "Cambrai, City Hall IT department",
        "experience.job2.date": "<strong>1 month</strong> - June 2021 to July 2021",
        "experience.job2.title": "IT technician intern",
        "experience.job2.desc.p1": "I had the privilege of undertaking a pivotal internship within the IT department of Cambrai City Hall. During this tenure, I was immersed in the city's IT operations, playing a vital role in maintaining and evolving Cambrai's IT infrastructure. My core responsibilities encompassed:",
        "experience.job2.desc.p2": "<li>Actively assisting and supporting the IT department staff in their daily tasks.</li><li>Participating in deploying solutions to optimize the existing infrastructure and ensure its long-term viability.</li><li>Collaborating closely with technical teams to understand and address the city's specific requirements.</li><li>Managing projects and responsibilities of such magnitude that they had never been entrusted to an intern before.</li>",
        "experience.job2.desc.p3": "This internship provided me with a unique opportunity to delve into the real challenges of a municipal IT service and make a substantial contribution to Cambrai's digital transformation.",

        "experience.job3.place": "Cambrai, City Hall IT department",
        "experience.job3.date": "<strong>15 days</strong> - 2019",
        "experience.job3.title": "IT technician intern",
        "experience.job3.desc.p1": "I had the opportunity to undertake a 15-day discovery internship within the IT department of Cambrai City Hall. Although brief, this experience offered me an initial immersion into the realm of municipal IT. During this observational period, my activities included:",
        "experience.job3.desc.p2": "<li>Observing IT department staff as they carried out their daily tasks.</li><li>Gaining insights into the operation and challenges of Cambrai's IT infrastructure.</li><li>Attending internal meetings to grasp the city's specific IT challenges and needs.</li><li>Sitting in on technical training and update sessions to familiarize myself with the tools and technologies in use.</li>",
        "experience.job3.desc.p3": "This discovery internship served as a valuable introduction to the IT challenges faced by a municipality and set the stage for my subsequent in-depth internship at Cambrai.",

        "projects.title": "Personal Projects",
        "projects.description": "This section provides an overview of my personal projects.",

        "projects.project0.title": "PotBlog",
        "projects.project0.date": "2025",
        "projects.project0.desc": "PotBlog is a personal project that I started in 2025. It is a blog platform that will allow me to share my thoughts, experiences, and projects with the world. I am currently developing the platform from scratch, including a custom Markdown to HTML parser and a user-friendly interface.",
        "projects.project0.tech": "Go, HTMX, Tailwind, SQLite, Docker, Figma",

        "projects.project1.title": "letterboxd-statistics",
        "projects.project1.date": "2024",
        "projects.project1.desc": "letterboxd-statistics is a personal project that I started in 2024. It is a website that allows users to visualize movie statistics of the most popular movies on Letterboxd. The website uses the scraping of the Letterboxd website every 5 minutes to update the statistics of the movies.",
        "projects.project1.tech": "Go, HTMX, Redis, Docker",

        "projects.project2.title": "letterboxd-jellyfin",
        "projects.project2.date": "2024",
        "projects.project2.desc": "letterboxd-jellyfin is small utility that I developed in 2024. It allows users to synchronize their Letterboxd watchlist with their Jellyfin server. I developed the utility first in Python but then rewrote it in Go for better performance and maintainability.",
        "projects.project2.tech": "Go, Python",

        "projects.project3.title": "ugc-alerts",
        "projects.project3.date": "2023",
        "projects.project3.desc": "ugc-alerts is a personal project that I started in 2023. It is a website that allows users to receive notifications when a movie is added to the UGC Cinéma program. The website uses the scraping of the UGC website to monitor the program and send notifications to the users via Discord.",
        "projects.project3.tech": "Python, Docker",

        "projects.project4.title": "Meledio",
        "projects.project4.date": "2022 -- 2024",
        "projects.project4.desc": "Meledio is a personal project that I started in 2022. It is the world 1st video game music streaming service. It allows users to listen to their favorite video game soundtracks, create playlists, and discover new music. I developed the entire platform from scratch, including the front-end, back-end, and database. The main challenges I faced were the construction of a large database of video game soundtracks, the implementation of a user-friendly interface on mobile and desktop, and the management of a growing codebase.",
        "projects.project4.tech": "Vuejs, Tailwind, Python, FastAPI, PostgreSQL, Docker, Figma",

        "projects.project5.title": "Gameinbox",
        "projects.project5.date": "2021",
        "projects.project5.desc": "Gameinbox is a personal project that I started in 2021. It is a Public dashboard of a Minecraft server's statistics and player activity. It contains the personal statistics of all the players and the general statistics of the server (number of players, performance of the server). It also contains the documentation of the server to help the players and a page containing the offers of the shops available on the server.",
        "projects.project5.tech": "HTML, CSS, JavaScript",

        "projects.project6.title": "Meridian",
        "projects.project6.date": "2025 -- Present",
        "projects.project6.desc": "Meridian is an open-source, graph-based platform for building, visualizing, and interacting with complex AI workflows. Instead of traditional linear chats, Meridian uses a visual canvas where you can connect different AI models, data sources, and logic blocks to create powerful and dynamic conversational agents.",
        "projects.project6.tech": "Nuxt, Vue, Tailwind, Python, FastAPI, PostgreSQL, Neo4j, Docker",
    },
